Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Boop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are you doing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can't fall back asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, fortunately, coffee exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't worry, I put\Nin blasphemous amounts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of cream in sugar just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice Weiss strikes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- I will pour this on\Nyou and it will burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can't believe we're actually in Mistral.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's what you can't believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the other magic and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But okay, you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- I honestly wasn't sure if\NI'd ever see you two again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, here's to defying expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- I just wish Blake could be here with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Yang] Yeah, well, she made her choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- I mean she could've been\Nhere if she just stuck around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't you want her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why would I want her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you still mad at her for leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, whatever gave you that idea, Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm totally fine, I'm great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't tell me to calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Whoa, Yang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Yang] Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Sun] Hey, Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- We going recruiting or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got the entire\Nnocturnal section to hit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, I'll meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to take care of something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look Ruby, I really don't\Nwant to talk about it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you just leave me alone for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Weiss, did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she's our teammate,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not just going to change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I just, I don't think you know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what it's like to be left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a giant family,\Nrecitals to perform at,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,dinners to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby's mom left too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tai was always busy with school
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and Ruby couldn't even talk yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to pick up the pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to keep things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Weiss, if you have something\Nto say, then say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- When I was 10 my dad finally\Nadmitted to my mom that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the only reason he married\Nher was for the family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was actually on my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He missed the big dinner, she\Ngot mad, he finally snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back, I think I knew too,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but hearing him say it finally\Npushed her over the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,First it was separate lunches and dinners,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,opposite balconies at my recitals,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a glass of wine here,\Na glass of wine there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, it was no dinners, no\Nrecitals, a bottle of wine here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and, well, you get the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm really sorry, I\Nshouldn't have assumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're right though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know loneliness like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my own version, and,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet Blake has her own version, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- She doesn't have to be alone though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was here for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We all were!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She chose to leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why do you think she did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire time Blake was at Beacon,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,she was afraid to open up to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She tried to keep her\Npast separated from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She tried to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, those walls\Nshe put up came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the moment they did, the one thing she
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,was afraid of actually happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The universe proved her right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- No one blamed her for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If she had just talked to\Nus, she would've known that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I be there for\Nher if she doesn't let me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I needed her here for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- I know it's not easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish she hadn't left, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing we can do now is be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,there for her when she's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When she comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- If she comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- She will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yang, you, Ruby, and even Blake are more
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,like family to me than my\Nbrother or even my own father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I would do anything for you three
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm willing to bet\NBlake feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when she's ready\NI'll be there for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:09:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know we're not as close,\Nbut, I'm here for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is, uh, everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ilia] I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ilia, I know you're scared\Nbut you don't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My family and I, we can keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can make it up to me by
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:10:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,helping us stop Corsac and Fennec.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well done, Sister\NTrifa, and to you, Ilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ilia, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- I tried to warn you, Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't tell me you're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- But I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry it has to be this way
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but you and your family are\Nholding the Faunas back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Because we're trying to protect people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In what world do you\Nlive in where attacking
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocent is the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- The same one as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no right thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Only what's best for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the humans that\Nstill hate the Faunus,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's the others who stand\Nby and let the hate happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know what snuffs out hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like hurting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll tell you this:\Nit's gotten us results.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, look where it's gotten you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- We all have to make\Nsacrifices for the greater good,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how much it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- And you think killing me is\Nreally for the greater good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, but getting rid of your family is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- You wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're being sent to Mistral.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ilia, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess back then you were just too
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,busy falling for Adam to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always jealous of\Nthe way you looked at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to look at me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't always get what we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuma, with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, get her to the docks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go, traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks for the backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks for the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard Ilia, my family is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the police and let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on, Mom, pick up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get out of my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghira!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go find my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- I believe it's time our dear
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,chieftain stepped down, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes brother, I'm afraid\NI'm inclined to agree.
